# Exploration: paste

## Rounds
  round 0: 11 isolated cumulative, 21 identical in round (discovery)
  round 1: 29 isolated cumulative, 9 identical in round (refinement)
  round 2: 29 isolated cumulative, 10 identical in round (refinement)

## Distinguished: 3/3 flags (3 observed behavior)
  3 observed behavior (3 solo, 0 via combination)

Aliases: -d = --delimiters, -s = --serial, -z = --zero-terminated

## Solo (unique behavior)
  -d  # reuse characters from LIST instead of TABs
    exemplar: "-d" "input.txt" "other.txt" in alpha_minimal (-1 lines)
    base:
      cherry	hello world
      Apple	
      banana	
      Date	
      elderberry	
            ...
    flag:
      hello world
  -s  # paste one file at a time instead of in parallel
    exemplar: "-s" in alpha_minimal (different)
    base:
    flag:
  -z  # line delimiter is NUL, not newline
    exemplar: "-z" "input.txt" "other.txt" in alpha_minimal (-10 lines)
    base:
      cherry	hello world
      Apple	
      banana	
      Date	
      elderberry	
            ...
    flag:
      cherry
      Apple
      banana
      Date
      elderberry
            ...

